These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, reading, skydiving, writing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, martial-arts, satire
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, alhambra, fonseca, oliveros
1. the chaman-smoker is the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is in an odd position##4
4. the alhambra-smoker is on the left or right of the oliveros-smoker##3
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
6. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
7. the alhambra-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
8. the oliveros-smoker is between the person watching satire movies and the person who's hobby is hiking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby         | writing      | hiking | reading | skydiving |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | crime  | drama   | satire    |
| Cigar     | chaman     | fonseca    | oliveros    | alhambra      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, singing, sudoku, video-games
There are 4 different nationalities: american, japanese, mexican, polish
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, thriller, time-travel, scientific
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is the mexican##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
4. the person watching documentary movies is on the far right##1
5. the person watching scientific movies is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the japanese##1
7. the american is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is singing##2
8. the polish is between the japanese and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | video-games | sudoku   | singing | dancing  |
| Nationality   | mexican     | american | polish  | japanese |
| Movie-Genre     | scientific        | time-travel  | thriller    | documentary |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, kiwi, lemon, tomato
House: ranch-style, craftsman, tower, modern
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, roller, snowmobile, train
1. the modern house is between the person eating grapefruit and the person eating tomato##2
2. the craftsman house is the person driving the train##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is the person eating lemon##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
5. the person eating tomato is in an odd position##4
6. the tower house is between the person eating kiwi and the ranch-style house##2
7. the modern house is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | grapefruit | kiwi   | tomato     | lemon     |
| House   | craftsman  | modern | tower   | ranch-style  |
| Transport     | train      | roller | snowmobile | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, taxi, helicopter, skateboard
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, punk, salsa, soul
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, rowing, tennis, water-polo
1. the fan of soul is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the taxi is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
5. the fan of soul is the person who's sport is badminton##1
6. the person driving the helicopter is the fan of pop##1
7. the fan of salsa is the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Transport   | van  | skateboard   | helicopter     | taxi |
| Music-Genre   | salsa  | soul      | pop        | punk     |
| Sport         | tennis | badminton | water-polo | rowing   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, canadian, colombian, japanese
4 different pets are kept: lizard, horse, hedgehog, guinea-pig
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, jet-ski, van
1. the japanese is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the colombian is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the bus is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the person driving the bus is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1
7. the canadian is on the far right##1
8. the colombian is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
9. the owner of the lizard is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | american   | japanese   | colombian | canadian |
| Pet         | horse      | guinea-pig | lizard      | hedgehog |
| Transport     | helicopter | bus        | van       | jet-ski  |

