.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, collecting, drawing, singing
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, librarian, scientist, social-worker
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, december, august, january
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
2. the scientist is the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the social-worker is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is between the journalist and the person who's hobby is chess##2
6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the scientist##3
7. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is drawing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | collecting | chess      | drawing       | singing    |
| Job           | librarian  | scientist  | social-worker | journalist |
| Birthday   | january      | august | december         | september    |

