.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, fanta, sprite
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, australian, pakistani, turkish
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, soul, salsa, folk
1. the fan of soul is between the person drinking fanta and the argentine##2
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
3. the pakistani is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
4. the fan of folk is on the left of the australian##1
5. the fan of folk is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
7. the argentine is on the left or right of the turkish##3
8. the pakistani is the person drinking almond-milk##1
9. the turkish is between the fan of salsa and the fan of gospel##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | fanta      | coffee  | sprite    |
| Nationality   | pakistani   | australian | turkish | argentine |
| Music-Genre           | folk      | salsa       | soul   | gospel      |

