The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, february, october, july
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, car, snowmobile
1. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
2. the person who's birthday is in august is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
5. the person drinking milk is between the person driving the bike and the person who's birthday is in october##2
6. the person driving the airplane is the person who's birthday is in july##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
8. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage    | mirinda    | milk     | cola    | tea        |
| Birthday       | october   | august | february | july |
| Transport   | snowmobile | car      | bike    | airplane   |

